### Get All Categories (Paged)
GET {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/category?pageIndex=1&pageSize=5&status=active
Accept: application/json

### Get Category by ID
GET {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/category/id/1
Accept: application/json

### Get Category by Slug
GET {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/category/dien-thoai
Accept: application/json

### Create Category (Admin)
POST {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Electronics",
  "status": "active"
}

### Update Category (Admin)
PUT {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Smartphones",
  "status": "active"
}

### Delete Category (Admin)
DELETE {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
